---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="KeepCalmAI | Calm Today. Confident Tomorrow."
  description="A calm, accessible way to learn AI one small step at a time."
>
  <Hero
    eyebrow="AI learning without overwhelm"
    title="Calm Today. Confident Tomorrow."
    text="KeepCalmAI helps people understand and use AI through short, practical learning journeys that build confidence one step at a time."
    ctaText="Start with AI Without Overwhelm"
    ctaHref="#start"
  />

  <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="why-title">
    <p class="eyebrow">Why KeepCalmAI?</p>
    <h2 id="why-title">Built for people who feel unsure, excluded or behind</h2>
    <p class="lead">Most AI training assumes confidence before it has been earned. KeepCalmAI starts from the opposite place: calm explanation, familiar examples and small practical steps.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="approach-title">
    <p class="eyebrow">The approach</p>
    <h2 id="approach-title">Small steps, clear progress</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <Card title="One idea at a time" text="Each step focuses on a single concept so the learner is not faced with a long page of information." />
      <Card title="Try it quickly" text="Every journey includes practical activities that help the learner use AI rather than only read about it." />
      <Card title="Confidence first" text="Progress is measured by whether the learner feels clearer, calmer and able to try the next step." />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="start" class="lesson-card" aria-labelledby="journey-title">
    <p class="eyebrow">First journey</p>
    <h2 id="journey-title">AI Without Overwhelm</h2>
    <p>This first journey introduces AI in short beginner-friendly steps. It explains what AI is, where it may already appear in everyday life, how to ask a first question, and why checking answers matters.</p>
    <div class="try-box">
      <h3>Designed to feel manageable</h3>
      <p>The journey is built as a sequence of small steps rather than one long article.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-box">
      <h3>Current status</h3>
      <p>The journey content and prototype exist in the repository. The next phase is to convert it fully into Astro routes and components.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
